        <section name="Introduction">
            <p>Force Field X is a group of open, platform independent modules for
               molecular biophysics. Modules include state-of-the-art force fields,
               electrostatics algorithms, methods for X-ray crystallography
               refinement and structure based drug design.
            </p>
